headline: GEHC Launches AI-Powered Vivid Pioneer Cardiac Ultrasound System

headline: FDA Identifies ICU Medical's Plum Duo Recall as Serious Type
summary: ICUI faces an FDA recall of its Plum Duo Infusion System over software flaws, though devices remain in use, pending fixes.
